                <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/opinion/letters/letter-protestors-prioritize-human-rights-so-should-we/article_6fb24ea0-0972-11ef-8fec-03193434eb25.html" class="tnt-asset-link" aria-label="Letter: Protestors prioritize human rights. So should we">
        
        
            Letter: Protestors prioritize human rights. So should we</a></h3></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">In Jonah Goldberg’s op-ed, “What we keep getting wrong about campus protests," May 2, I strongly disagree with his assertion that “democratic will is exercised by private actions of individual voters casting secret ballots, not strength in numbers invoked by large protests.” </p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
