                <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/opinion/letters/letter-kinship-care-benefits-children-in-foster-system/article_a79ad666-07dd-11ef-96eb-4fb502001b10.html" class="tnt-asset-link" aria-label="Letter: Kinship care benefits children in foster system">
        
        
            Letter: Kinship care benefits children in foster system</a></h3></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">The recent passing of House Bill 27 has sparked a great deal of interest and curiosity regarding how this bill benefits the children in foster care. </p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
