        <div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/opinion/letters/letter-tiktok-ban-will-safeguard-families/article_1d326430-071a-11ef-b0ef-f3564d1c584e.html" class="tnt-asset-link" aria-label="Letter: TikTok ban will safeguard families">
        
        
            Letter: TikTok ban will safeguard families</a></h3></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">In today’s digital world, safeguarding our children from harmful online content is more important than ever. As a grandfather to six young children, I understand firsthand the importance of ensuring our children’s safety online. </p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
