                <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-headline"><h4 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/opinion/letters/letter-stop-legislative-attacks-on-transgender-youth/article_386c3756-03de-11ef-b5bf-c311702292af.html" class="tnt-asset-link" aria-label="Letter: Stop legislative attacks on transgender youth">
        
        
            Letter: Stop legislative attacks on transgender youth</a></h4></div>
    <div class="card-meta">
                <ul class="list-inline"></ul>
            </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">Eleven anti-transgender bills were introduced in Virginia’s General Assembly during the 2024 session. While all of these bills were defeated, their introduction highlights a persistent threat to the rights and safety of Virginia’s transgender youth. This marks the second consecutive session &hellip;</p>
