                <ul class="list-inline"></ul>
            </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">Virginia is currently one of the only Southern states that has not passed any legislation or policies that ban gender-affirming health care. Research shows that gender-affirming health care is medically necessary, and lifesaving in some instances, for transgender youth and adults alike. Unac&hellip;</p>
