            </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">As a concerned resident of Richmond, I am compelled to address the alarming escalation of gun violence that plagues our city. The pervasive nature of community gun violence inflicts an enormous burden upon our communities, particularly those that are under-resourced. The health and well-bein&hellip;</p>
