            Letter: Liver disease treatment is finally available</a></h4></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">April 29 is the first World Liver Day that millions of patients with a common liver disease can celebrate with the knowledge that a drug is finally available to treat their disease. </p>
