                </a>
                
            </div>
            
        </figure></div>
                    </div>
                
                <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-headline"><h4 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/opinion/letters/letter-israel-fails-to-achieve-goals-in-gaza/article_42c7190e-f683-11ee-a673-3b6ab81b6962.html" class="tnt-asset-link" aria-label="Letter: Israel fails to achieve goals in Gaza">
        
        
            Letter: Israel fails to achieve goals in Gaza</a></h4></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">After six months of war in Gaza, the two forces seem to have reached a stalemate. Israel has not lost the war, but it certainly has failed to achieve its goals. The two objectives it had announced at the beginning of the invasion into Gaza were the elimination of Hamas and the liberation of &hellip;</p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </article>
                    
                    
