            Letter: Dominion is not addressing the climate crisis</a></h4></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">The article, “9 legislators oppose Dominion gas plant plan,” March 13, omits an important reason stated in the legislators’ statement: Dominion Energy’s long range plans including this Chesterfield gas plant “would actually increase carbon emissions from the 21.8 million metric tons emitted &hellip;</p>
